      "The Marylebone location, when the hotel is open, is one of its quieter strengths. Chiltern Street has emerged over the past decade as one of central London's most concentrated independent retail streets (Trunk, Monocle, The Conran Shop's former Marylebone space, Jack Wills). The Wallace Collection is five minutes' walk, Regent's Park eight minutes, Marylebone High Street three. Baker Street station is four minutes.",
